eries)|The Zoo]]''\n{{colend}}\n\n====Reality====\n{{Div col}}\n* ''[[The Amazing Race (U.S. TV series)|The Amazing Race]]''<ref name=\"7flixschedulelaunch\"/><ref name=\"PrimeTVTonight\"/>\n* ''[[Australian Spartan]]''\n* ''[[Back with the Ex]]''\n* ''[[Bride & Prejudice (TV series)|Bride & Prejudice]]''\n* ''[[First Dates (Australia)]]''<ref name=\"ontheair\"/>\n* ''[[First Dates|First Dates (UK)]]''\n* ''[[House Rules (Australian TV series)|House Rules]]''<ref name=\"14May2017\"/>\n* ''[[The Mentor (TV series)|The Mentor]]''\n* ''[[My Kitchen Rules]]''\n* ''[[Whodunnit? (2013 U.S. TV series)|Whodunnit?]]''\n* ''[[Yummy Mummies]]''\n* ''[[Zumbo's Just Desserts]]''\n{{colend}}\n\n====Religious====\n* ''[[Life Today with James Robison]]''\n\n===Former programming===\n====Children's====\n{{Div col}}\n* ''[[The 7D]]'' (2016\u201318)\n* ''[[A.N.T. Farm]]'' (2016\u201317)\n* ''[[Austin & Ally]]''<ref name=\"SDEnd2016\"/> (2016\u201318)\n* ''[[Best Friends Whenever]]'' (2017\u201319)\n* ''[[Crash & Bernstein]]'' (2016\u201318)\n* ''[[Dog with a Blog]]''<ref name=\"SDEnd2016\"/> (2016\u201319)\n* ''[[Drop Dead Weird]]'' (2017\u201318)\n* ''[[The Evermoor Chronicles]]'' (2017\u201319)\n* ''[[Fish Hooks]]'' (2016\u201317)\n* ''[[Gamer's Guide to Pretty Much Everything]]'' (2016\u201319)\n* ''Get Arty'' (2018\u201319)\n* ''[[Girl Meets World]]'' (2017\u201319)\n* ''[[Good Luck Charlie]]'' (2016\u201317)\n* ''[[Gravity Falls]]'' (2016\u201319)\n* ''Hairy Legs'' (2018)\n* ''History Hunters'' (2017\u201318)\n* ''[[I Didn't Do It (TV series)|I Didn't Do It]]''<ref name=\"SDEnd2016\"/> (2016\u201319)\n* ''[[Jessie (2011 TV series)|Jessie]]''<ref name=\"SDEnd2016\"/> (2016\u201319)\n* ''[[K.C. Undercover]]'' (2016\u201318)\n* ''[[Kickin' It]]'' (2016\u201318)\n* ''[[Kirby Buckets]]''<ref name=\"SDEnd2016\"/> (2016\u201319)\n* ''[[Kitty Is Not a Cat|Kitty is Not a Cat]]'' (2018\u201319)\n* ''[[Lab Rats (U.S. TV series)|Lab Rats]]''<ref name=\"SDEnd2016\"/> (2016\u201319)\n* ''[[Liv and Maddie]]'' (2017\u201319)\n* ''[[Mighty Med]]''<ref name=\"SDEnd2016\"/> (2016\u201318)\n* ''Oh Yuck!'' (2017)\n* ''[[Max Adventures|Paddle Pop: Atlantos]]'' (2016)\n* ''[[Pair of Kings]]'' (2016\u201317)\n* ''[[Penn Zero: Part-Time Hero]]'' (2017\u201319)\n* ''[[Phineas and Ferb]]'' (2016\u201317)\n* ''[[Pickle and Peanut]]'' (2017\u201319)\n* ''[[Randy Cunningham: 9th Grade Ninja]]'' (2016\u201318)\n* ''[[Saturday Disney]]'' (2016)\n* ''[[Shake It Up (U.S. TV series)|Shake it Up]]'' (2016)\n* ''[[Star vs. the Forces of Evil]]'' (2017\u201319)\n* ''[[Star Wars Rebels]]'' (2017\u201318; moved to 9Go!)\n* ''[[Tashi (TV series)|Tashi]]'' (2018\u201319)\n* ''[[Wander Over Yonder]]'' (2017\u201319)\n* ''[[Win, Lose or Draw (2014 game show)|Win, Lose or Draw]]'' (2017)\n* ''The Woodlies'' (2017)\n* ''[[Zeke and Luther]]'' (2016)\n* ''[[ZooMoo]]'' (2018\u201319)\n{{colend}}\n\n====Preschool====\n{{Div col}}\n* ''[[Art Attack]]'' (2016\u201318)\n* ''[[Doc McStuffins]]'' (2016\u201319)\n* ''[[Henry Hugglemonster]]'' (2016\u201319)\n* ''[[Jake and the Never Land Pirates]]'' (2016\u201319)\n* ''[[The Lion Guard]]'' (2016\u201319; moved to 9Go!)\n* ''[[Mickey Mouse Clubhouse]]'' (2016\u201318)\n* ''[[Miles from Tomorrowland]]'' (2016\u201318)\n* ''[[Sheriff Callie's Wild West]]'' (2016\u201317)\n* ''[[Sofia the First]]'' (2016\u201319; moved to 9Go!)\n{{colend}}\n\n====Comedy====\n{{Div col}}\n* ''[[Agent Anna]]''\n* ''[[Bad Teacher (TV series)|Bad Teacher]]''<ref name=\"BadTeacher\"/>\n* ''[[Benson (TV series)|Benson]]''<ref name=\"ontheair\"/>\n* ''[[Bewitched]]''<ref name=\"ontheair\"/>\n* ''[[The Big Bang Theory]]''<ref name=\"BigBang\"/><ref name=\"BigBangEnd\">{{cite web|url=https://tvtonight.com.au/2018/01/nine-nabs-big-bang-episodes-back.html|title=Nine nabs ''Big Bang'' episodes back |date=22 January 2018|accessdate=25 January 2018|first=David|last=Knox|work=[[TV Tonight]]}}</ref> (2016\u201317; Now on Nine)\n* ''[[Black-ish]]''<ref name=\"multichannelsurvey2016\