-h-i-e-l-d-4.html|title=Returning: Marvel\u2019s Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. |date=24 February 2017|accessdate=24 February 2017|first=David|last=Knox|work=[[TV Tonight]]}}</ref><ref name=\"AgentsFeb2018\">{{cite web|url=https://tvtonight.com.au/2018/02/returning-marvels-agents-of-shield.html|title=Returning: Marvel\u2019s Agents of SHIELD |date=23 February 2018|accessdate=23 February 2018|first=David|last=Knox|work=[[TV Tonight]]}}</ref>\n* ''American Crime''\n* ''[[The Astronaut Wives Club]]''<ref name=\"Astronaut\"/>\n* ''[[Battle Creek (TV series)|Battle Creek]]''<ref name=\"4Jun2017\"/><ref name=\"multichannelsurvey2017\"/>\n* ''[[Betrayal (TV series)|Betrayal]]''\n* ''[[Blindspot (TV series)|Blindspot]]''\n* ''[[Body of Proof]]'' (2016\u201317)\n* ''[[Castle (TV series)|Castle]]''<ref name=\"4Jun2017\">{{cite web|url=https://mumbrella.com.au/7flix-program-schedule-week-commencing-june-4-2017-447255|title=7flix Program Schedule for Week Commencing June 4, 2017|date=29 May 2017|accessdate=31 May 2017|first=|last=|work=[[Mumbrella]]|publisher=Focal Attractions Pty Ltd}}</ref>\n* ''[[Code Black (TV series)|Code Black]]''<ref name=\"multichannelsurvey2017\">{{cite web|url=http://www.tvtonight.com.au/2017/06/multichannel-survey-7two-7mate-7flix.html |title= Multichannel Survey: 7TWO, 7mate, 7flix.|date=27 June 2017|accessdate=11 July 2017|first=David|last=Knox|work=TV Tonight}}</ref>\n* ''[[Covert Affairs]]'' (2016)\n* ''[[Criminal Minds: Beyond Borders]]''\n* ''[[Criminal Minds: Suspect Behavior]]''\n* ''[[Defiance (TV series)|Defiance]]''\n* ''[[The Good Doctor (TV series)|The Good Doctor]]'' (Now on Channel 7)\n* ''[[Grimm (TV series)|Grimm]]''\n* ''[[Hoges: The Paul Hogan Story]]''\n* ''[[Intelligence (U.S. TV series)|Intelligence]]''\n* ''[[Liar (TV series)|Liar]]''\n* ''[[Mistresses (U.S. TV series)|Mistresses]]''\n* ''[[Molly (miniseries)|Molly]]'' (2016)\n* ''[[Motive (TV series)|Motive]]'' (2016)\n* ''[[American Odyssey|Odyssey]]''\n* ''[[Once Upon a Time (TV ser