ral]] ||23 October 1907 || 19 March 1908 || {{age in years and days|1907|10|23|1908|3|19}} || L\u00f8vland\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:KarlSeip1855.jpg|100x100px]]\n! scope=row | [[Karl Seip]]\n| style=\"background:#AEE8A8\" | [[Liberal Party (Norway)|Liberal]] ||19 March 1908 || 8 July 1909 || {{age in years and days|1908|3|19|1909|7|8}} || Knudsen I\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Knut johannes hougen.jpg|100x100px]]\n! scope=row | [[Knut Johannes Hougen|Johannes Hougen]]\n| style=\"background:#AEE8A8\" | [[Liberal Party (Norway)|Liberal]] ||8 July 1909 || 2 February 1910 || {{age in years and days|1909|7|8|1910|2|2}} || Knudsen I\n|-\n| align=center |  [[File:Just Qvigstad.jpg|100x100px]] \n! scope=row | [[Just Qvigstad]]\n| style=\"background:#AACCFF\" | [[Conservative Party (Norway)|Conservative]] || 2 February 1910 || 20 February 1912 || {{age in years and days|1910|2|2|1912|2|20}} || Konow\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Edvard liljedahl cropped.jpg|100x100px]]\n! scope=row | [[Edvard Liljedahl]]\n| style=\"background:#ADD8E6\" | [[Free-minded Liberal Party|Free-minded Liberal]] || 20 February 1912 || 31 January 1913 || {{age in years and days|1912|2|20|1913|1|31}} || [[Bratlie's Cabinet|Bratlie]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Aasulv_Bryggesaa.jpg|100x100px]]\n! scope=row | [[Aasulv Olsen Bryggesaa|Aasulv Bryggesaa]]\n| style=\"background:#AEE8A8\" | [[Liberal Party (Norway)|Liberal]] ||31 January 1913 || 26 October 1915 || {{age in years and days|1913|1|3|1915|10|26}} || Knudsen II\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:J._L\u00f8vland_-_no-nb_digifoto_20160420_00234_NB_NS_NM_10313_(cropped).jpg|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[J\u00f8rgen L\u00f8vland]]\n| style=\"background:#AEE8A8\" | [[Liberal Party (Norway)|Liberal]] || 26 October 1915 || 21 June 1920 || {{age in years and days|1915|10|26|1920|6|21}} || Knudsen II\n|-\n| align=center |  [[File:Nils Riddervold Jensen.jpg|100x100px]] \n! scope=row | [[Nils Riddervold Jensen]]\n| style=\"background:#AACCFF\" | [[Conservative Party